## App Manifest Configuration

The `manifest.json` defines app locations and settings:

```json
{
  "name": "Quick Info Dashboard",
  "target_type": "stack",
  "ui_location": {
    "signed": false,
    "base_url": "http://localhost:3000",
    "locations": [
      {
        "type": "cs.cm.stack.dashboard",
        "meta": [
          {
            "path": "/stack-dashboard",
            "enabled": true,
            "default_width": "half"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

